reviewText: What can I say, if you haven't seen Saturdays Warrior, you are missing out, if you haven't seen it in a while, you'll love it again. I watched it as a child and it totally has a greater meaning for me now as an adult/parent. Yes, I know parts are really cheesy, but I love that type of show. It's funny and has great meaning. The extra footage is great. Share it with your children!
